<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="message-sm">
            <h1>Your ELearning order is confirmed!</h1>
            <p>And we're just as excited as you are.</p>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div class="course-info">
            <h4>Here's what you ordered:</h4>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td>Order #: <%= order._id %></td>
                    <td>Order Date: <%= order.date %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td>Item</td>
                    <td>Qty</td>
                    <td>cost</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td><%= order.name %></td>
                    <td>1</td>
                    <td><%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td>Subtotal:</td>
                    <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td>Total:</td>
                    <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any question, please contact our support team at
                <a href="mailto:ngocduc8122002@gmail.com">ngocduc8122002@gmail.com</a>
            </p>
            <p>&copy; 2023 ELearning. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>